cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SE 

This paper deals with the security of deep neural networks, specifically backdoor attacks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves training and fine-tuning of DNNs, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning). The attacks and defenses are evaluated on image classification tasks, which falls under cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also involves the use of DNNs, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves the implementation and evaluation of defenses, which falls under cs.SE (Software Engineering).
